{"product_id":"gods-favourite","title":"GOD'S FAVOURITE","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eCLOTH : 260 GSM FRENCH TERRY\r\nFIT : BOXY\r\nFRONT PRINT : EMBROIDERY\r\nBACK PRINT : EMBROIDERY\r\nQUALITY : COMBED \u0026amp; BIOWASHED\r\n\r\n\" MODEL HEIGHT 5'10, WEARING M SIZE \"\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStep into effortless streetwear energy with our Collar Oversized Tee—crafted for those who let their style speak louder than words. Featuring a bold front chest banding print with “DRIPSTU.”, this piece carries that clean, premium edge your fits have been waiting for. The back flex? A powerful “GODS FAVOURITE” statement print, dropping an unapologetic vibe that turns every sidewalk into a runway.\r\n\r\nCut in an oversized fit with structured collar detailing, this tee brings a mix of comfort and authority, making it perfect for pairing with cargos, denims, or shorts. Built from heavyweight cotton for durability and luxe feel, it’s more than just a tee—it’s a declaration.\r\n\r\nHighlights:\r\n\r\nOversized streetwear fit with collar\r\nFront chest DRIPSTU. banding print\r\nBack print: “GODS FAVOURITE” bold statement\r\nHeavyweight cotton, soft yet durable\r\n\r\nDesigned for all-day wear \u0026amp; elevated drip\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the vest inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the vest in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eVest with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"t